OL,3,CWhy are equal pay claims sweeping
OL,4,Ccouncils across the UK?
OL,6,FITV News' Deputy Political Editor
OL,7,FAnushka Asthana looks at the issues
OL,8,Fwhich caused Birmingham City Council's
OL,9,Fequal pay scandal and why similar
OL,10,Fclaims are being lodged with other
OL,11,Fcouncils across the UK.
OL,13,FAs Birmingham Council finally settles
OL,14,Fan equal pay scandal, which its leader
OL,15,Fadmitted to me today has "dogged" the
OL,16,Flocal authority for years, similar
OL,17,Fcases are being repeated across the
OL,18,Fcountry.
