OL,3,CWhy are equal pay claims sweeping
OL,4,Ccouncils across the UK?
OL,6,FBirmingham's decision to pay out
OL,7,Fcompensation follows a similar move in
OL,8,FGlasgow and there are now live equal
OL,9,Fpay cases in five other councils in
OL,10,FScotland, two in Wales, and across
OL,11,FEngland from Cumbria, Leeds and
OL,12,FSheffield, to further south in
OL,13,FBristol, Coventry, and along the coast
OL,14,Fin Brighton and Southampton.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
