OL,3,CWhy are equal pay claims sweeping
OL,4,Ccouncils across the UK?
OL,6,FFor example, in Birmingham, one issue
OL,7,F- comparing TA's and others to refuse
OL,8,Fcollectors - is not overall salary,
OL,9,Fbut perks for the male dominated roles
OL,10,Flike "task and finish" which allow men
OL,11,Fto finish a set number of tasks and
OL,12,Fthen go home, whatever the hours,
OL,13,Finflating their hourly pay.
OL,15,FIn fact, the legal challenge showed
OL,16,Fthat refuse collectors could receive
OL,17,Fdouble the hourly pay than teaching
OL,18,Fassistants in comparable roles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
