OL,3,CWhy are equal pay claims sweeping
OL,4,Ccouncils across the UK?
OL,6,FSimilar perks can be found everywhere,
OL,7,Fas can straightforward salary
OL,8,Fdifferences.
OL,10,FThe GMB union has been at the
OL,11,Fforefront of trying to launch cases
OL,12,Faround the country to highlight the
OL,13,Finjustices, with councils (unlike some
OL,14,Fof their corporate targets) often
OL,15,Fadmitting quite quickly that there is
OL,16,Fa problem to be fixed.
OL,18,FBut it is a problem that brings huge
OL,19,Fethical questions, for two key reasons.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
