OL,3,CWhy are equal pay claims sweeping
OL,4,Ccouncils across the UK?
OL,6,FThe first is that councils are
OL,7,Fdelivering local services all over the
OL,8,Fcountry, so when they are hit with a
OL,9,Fmassive financial penalty, it affects
OL,10,Fall of us.
OL,12,FBirmingham had argued in 2023 that
OL,13,Fequal pay was a major factor in them
OL,14,Fissuing a section 114 notice
OL,15,F(effectively admitting they were
OL,16,Fhurtling towards bankruptcy).
OL,18,FThis led to massive council tax hikes,
OL,19,F21% over two years, alongside
OL,20,Fsignificant cuts to services.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
