OL,3,CWhy are equal pay claims sweeping
OL,4,Ccouncils across the UK?
OL,6,FJean Cross, who is a full-time carer
OL,7,Fto her disabled brother, is furious
OL,8,Fthat the day centre he goes to each
OL,9,Fday, giving her respite, is set to
OL,10,Fclose in March because of the huge
OL,11,Fcuts.
OL,13,FThat is not to mention the savings
OL,14,Fthat will need to be made on bin
OL,15,Fcollection, grass cutting, leisure
OL,16,Fcentres, and even the core provision
OL,17,Fof adult and children's social care.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
