OL,3,CWhy are equal pay claims sweeping
OL,4,Ccouncils across the UK?
OL,6,FAnd then there is the second thorny
OL,7,Fissue. If councils have to deal with
OL,8,Fthis, and they are already facing
OL,9,Ffinancial pressure, do they opt to
OL,10,Fpull down the men's perks, rather than
OL,11,Fraise up the women?
OL,13,FIn Birmingham, part of the case made
OL,14,Fwas that the comparators to the TA's,
OL,15,Fcarers and cleaners - who worked in
OL,16,Fwaste and refuse - were being placed
OL,17,Fin grade 3 roles while their actual
OL,18,Ftasks did not justify it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
