OL,3,CWhy are equal pay claims sweeping
OL,4,Ccouncils across the UK?
OL,6,FThe council has moved to abolish that
OL,7,Frole, moving many of the male workers
OL,8,Fonto genuine grade 3 alternatives -
OL,9,Feven if extra training is required.
OL,11,FBut some face being downgraded as a
OL,12,Fresult, something that has led a
OL,13,Fdifferent union, Unite, to ballot its
OL,14,Fmembers to strike.
