OL,3,CWhy are equal pay claims sweeping
OL,4,Ccouncils across the UK?
OL,6,FMoreover, it is trade unions
OL,7,Fthemselves that have often negotiated
OL,8,Fthe perks in some of the roles now
OL,9,Fbeing used to argue discrimination
OL,10,Fagainst women.
OL,12,FAnd so the complexities of this issue
OL,13,Fgo on - as councils seek to right
OL,14,Fhistoric injustices while knowing they
OL,15,Fcan impact on residents and workers in
OL,16,Fmale-dominated roles.
OL,18,FIt may be why not all local
OL,19,Fauthorities are jumping to solve their
OL,20,Fissues.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
