OL,6,FI'm told some are quite hostile to the
OL,7,Funions when cases are brought. Which
OL,8,Fis why this issue is likely to
OL,9,Fcontinue to spread and cause a serious
OL,10,Fheadache for councils and the Labour
OL,11,Fgovernment.
